# VaxViz
This repo covers the code for website with vizualization of Vaccination data from [UNICEF](https://data.unicef.org/resources/data_explorer/unicef_f/?ag=UNICEF&df=GLOBAL_DATAFLOW&ver=1.0&_REG_GLOBAL+WHO_AFRO+WHO_AMRO+WHO_EMRO+WHO_EURO+WHO_SEARO+WHO_WPRO.IMMUNISATION+IM_DTP1+ED_ATTND_FRML_INST+ED_15-24_LR+ECON_GVT_HLTH_EXP_PTEXP+ECON_GVT_HLTH_EXP_PTGDP+DM_POP_TOT+DM_POP_U5+CME_MRY0T4+CME_COVID_DEATHS+CME_COVID_CASES+IM_DTP3+IM_HEPB3+IM_HEPBB+IM_HIB3+IM_IPV1+IM_MCV1+IM_MCV2+IM_PAB+IM_PCV3+IM_POL3+IM_RCV1+IM_ROTAC+PV_CHLD_DPRV-L1-HS+PV_CHLD_DPRV-L5-HS+PV_CHLD_INCM-PL+PV_LEVEL+PV_GAP..&startPeriod=1960&endPeriod=2023) as part of Data Visualization course for Masterâ€™s in Data Science degree from UC Berkeley.

The website is live at [https://groups.ischool.berkeley.edu/VaxViz/](https://groups.ischool.berkeley.edu/VaxViz/).
